│  Economic Powers Act). Trump called the decision "deeply disappointing" at a press conference earlier       │
│  today while planning to push for new 10% global tariffs as an alternative. Nazak Nikakhtar, chair and      │
│  partner for Wiley Rein's National Security Practice, comes on Market Domination to help define the         │
│  executive branch's tariff authorities outlined in IEEPA and comment on whether SCOTUS could force the      │
│  administration to refund tariffs. Nikakhtar also served as the US Department of Commerce's Assistant       │
